{
  "texts": [
    "In order to do so, they re-train BERT with AAE tweets.",
    "Finally, adversarial training is needed to regulate the debiasing of the hate speech classifier.",
    "Specifically, the adversary takes the final representation learned by the hate-speech classifier, and learns to predict the dialect from it.",
    "Kaseb and Farouk [2022] present a dialect-aware approach for sarcasm detection called the SAIDS model.",
    "SAIDS uses MARBERT to detect dialect and sarcasm."
  ]
}